<h2>Seller Application Update</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<p>Thank you for your interest in selling on GhanaMarket. Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your application at this time.</p>

<div class="error-box">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b;">Reason:</p>
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #7f1d1d;">{{reason}}</p>
</div>

<p>You are welcome to address the issues above and submit a new application.</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{platformUrl}}/seller/register" class="btn">Submit New Application</a>
</div>

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px;">If you believe this was an error, please contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}.</p>
